{"analytics_identifier":"PB527","base_path":"/government/organisations/independent-reconfiguration-panel","content_id":"171abbf3-beca-46b9-a0c3-4b4ff1e8c8ed","description":"The IRP is a committee of experts who provide impartial specialist advice about proposals to change NHS services in England to support ministerial decisions. IRP is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department of Health and Social Care .","details":{"acronym":"IRP","alternative_format_contact_email":"IRPINFO@dhsc.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The IRP is a committee of experts who provide impartial specialist advice about proposals to change NHS services in England to support ministerial decisions.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Independent Reconfiguration Panel\">IRP</abbr> is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-of-health-and-social-care\">Department of Health and Social Care</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-of-health","foi_exempt":true,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Independent <br/>Reconfiguration Panel"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/independent-reconfiguration-panel/about/accessible-documents-policy","title":"Accessible documents policy"},{"href":"/government/organisations/independent-reconfiguration-panel/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"},{"href":"/government/organisations/independent-reconfiguration-panel/about/terms-of-reference","title":"Terms of reference"},{"href":"https://apply-for-public-appointment.service.gov.uk/roles","title":"Jobs"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Manual","href":"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2022/31/schedule/6","image":{"alt_text":"Health and Care Act 2022","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d3bc53e6b7941f4e00ab2/s712_Act_2022.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d3bc53e6b7941f4e00ab1/s465_Act_2022.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d3bc5c2633bd820a92a82/Act_2022.png"},"public_updated_at":"2024-01-31T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Act added a new discretionary power to the NHS Act 2006 for the Secretary of State to call in and make a decision on a reconfiguration proposal.</p>\n</div>","title":"Health and Care Act 2022: Intervention powers over the reconfiguration of NHS services"},{"document_type":"Statutory guidance","href":"/government/publications/reconfiguring-nhs-services-ministerial-intervention-powers","image":{"alt_text":"Reconfiguring NHS services - ministerial intervention powers","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d3a4961d68e6ee1a92a77/s712_DHSC_stautory_guidance.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d3a49e44db4975be00aa4/s465_DHSC_stautory_guidance.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d3a49f85b4b993fd752b7/DHSC_stautory_guidance.png"},"public_updated_at":"2024-01-31T00:01:01.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Guidance setting out the process for ministerial intervention in reconfiguration of NHS services, including when and how NHS commissioning bodies must notify the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care of NHS service changes.</p>\n</div>","title":"Reconfiguring NHS services - ministerial intervention powers"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/advice-to-local-authorities-on-scrutinising-health-services","image":{"alt_text":"Advice to local authorities on scrutinising health services","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d39ee61d68e6ee1a92a76/s712_DHSC_health_scrutiny_guidance.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d39ee61d68e6ee1a92a75/s465_DHSC_health_scrutiny_guidance.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.go